# Welcome to RESTAPI tutorial with fastapi

## Setting up the environment
1. You should have python3 installed in your system
2. Clone this repo
3. Go the the repo folder
4. Activate a python virtual environment `python3 -m venv venv`
5. Activate the virtual environment `. ./venv/bin/active`
6. Install all the packages `pip install -r requirements.txt`
7. Run the fastapi server `fastapi run main.py`
*You should have a running fastapi server
8. To see all the paths go to `http://localhost:8000/docs`
